Original Text: パンツ所持数など取得

Machine translation: \E\f[40]...Are you going to do it...that thing!!
Better translation: \E\font[3]\f[40]\-[2]...I suppose... I'm qualified to do that thing...!

Original Text: \Eパッと宙に舞う色とりどりのパンツ。

\E白、ピンク、水色…色とりどりのパンツ達は
色彩豊かなシャワーとなって宙を舞い降り注ぐ。
Machine translation:
\EWhite, pink, light blue... The colorful pants 
descend from the sky like a vibrant shower.
Better translation:
\E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]White, pink, light blue... The colorful pants 
descend from the sky like a vibrant shower.

Original Text:
\Eここにある全てが長年こつこつ集めてきたお宝たち。
一枚一枚に特別な想いが込められている…。
Machine translation:
\EAll the treasures gathered diligently over the years are here.
Each and every one of them holds special feelings within...
Better translation:
\E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]All the treasures gathered diligently over the years are here.
Each and every one of them holds special feelings within...

Original Text:
\E…ここまでの道のりは長く、
決して平たんな道ではなかった。
Machine translation:
\E...The journey up to this point has been long, and 
certainly not a smooth path.
Better translation:
\E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]...The journey up to this point has been long, and 
certainly not a smooth one.

Original Text:
\E手に取れば温もりと共に思い出が蘇る…
あの日、あの時、妹が身に着けていたパンツ。
Machine translation:
\EWhen I hold it, memories come back along with warmth...
That day, that time, the panties my sister was wearing.
Better translation:
\E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]When I hold it, memories come back along with warmth...
That day, that time, the panties my sister was wearing.

Original Text:
\Eそれはもはやただの布ではない、
これまで妹の生きてきた証であり人生の軌跡。
Machine translation:
\EIt is no longer just a piece of cloth, 
it is the proof of my sister's existence and the trajectory of her life.
Better translation:
\E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]It is no longer just a piece of cloth, 
it is the proof of my sister's existence and the trajectory of her life.

Original Text:
\E一枚一枚全てに特別で唯一の物語がある。
ひらめくパンツの合間からあの日の妹の姿が…思い出が蘇る…。
Machine translation:
\EEach and every one has a special and unique story.
From between the flashing panties, the figure of my sister from that day... memories come flooding back...
Better translation:
\E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]ach and every one has a special and unique story. From between the flickering panties, 
the image of my sister from that day emerges... Memories come flooding back...
\E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]I have no regrets in my life!!

Original Text: \Eスキル\c[1]探索上手\c[0]のヒントを得た！
